This is the Sysconf Configuration Management system. To test it, these
commands.

First, you must build needed script as this:

	$ make

Once it's done, you can run the demo script with the following commands:

1. Running the demo script by using the dialog frontend

	$ SYSCONF_FRONTEND=dialog ./frontend sample/demo

2. Running the demo script by using the teletype frontend

	SYSCONF_FRONTEND=teletype ./frontend sample/demo

3. Running the demo script by using the noninteractive frontend

	SYSCONF_FRONTEND=noninteractive ./frontend sample/demo
